text: Khalifa Karouane (1937 - before 1998) was a Moroccan wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 57 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Moroccan male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Morocco Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Casablanca
